#. Tag: title
#: locate.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate &GUI; Frontend"
msgstr "Grafiskt gränssnitt för locate"

#. Tag: primary
#: locate.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locate"
msgstr "Locate"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; has a &GUI; front end for the <command>locate</command> command "
"(findutils). Locate is used for fast file searching not from a folder but a "
"database. The package contains among other files, <command>locate</command> "
"and <command>updatedb</command>. <command>updatedb</command> goes through "
"the local file system and stores the file entries in the database. "
"<command>cron</command> often calls <command>updatedb</command> every night "
"(set with <application>KCron</application>). Choose <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locate...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
"or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to "
"start this feature. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> "
"can set additional arguments for <command>updatedb</command>."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; har ett grafiskt gränssnitt för kommandot <command>locate</"
"command> (i findutils). Locate används för snabb filsökning från en databas "
"istället för från en katalog. Paketet innehåller förutom andra filer, "
"<command>locate</command> och <command>updatedb</command>. "
"<command>updatedb</command> går igenom det lokala filsystemet och lagrar "
"filposterna i databasen. <command>cron</command> anropar ofta "
"<command>updatedb</command> varje natt (inställt med <application>Kcron</"
"application>). Välj <menuchoice><guimenu>Verktyg</guimenu>  "
"<guimenuitem>Lokalisera</guimenuitem></menuchoice> eller <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> för att starta "
"funktionen. <link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Konfigurator</link> kan ställa "
"in ytterligare argument för kommandot <command>updatedb</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checkbox Options"
msgstr "Alternativ i kryssrutor"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Show only the existing files</guilabel>: if the database contains "
"entries which no longer exist any more (deleted, moved since the last "
"<command>updatedb</command>), <command>locate</command> does not list them. "
"It checks the existence of each file before the listing in the results "
"window (slow)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Visa bara befintliga filer</guilabel>: Om databasen innehåller "
"poster som inte längre finns (borttagna, flyttade sedan den senaste "
"<command>updatedb</command>), listar inte <command>locate</command> dem. Den "
"kontrollerar om varje fil finns innan den listas i resultatfönstert "
"(långsamt)."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel>: unchecking it allows lower and upper "
"case search."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Skiftlägeskänslig</guilabel>: Att avmarkera alternativet tillåter "
"sökning med små och stora bokstäver."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action buttons"
msgstr "Åtgärdsknappar"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Locate</guibutton>: executes <command>locate <replaceable>foo "
"foo</replaceable></command> and places its output into the results window."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Lokalisera</guibutton>: kör <command>locate <replaceable>fil fil</"
"replaceable></command> och placerar utdata i resultatfönstret."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: stops the locating process."
msgstr "<guibutton>Stoppa</guibutton>: Stoppar lokaliseringsprocessen."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>UpdateDB</guibutton>: starts <command>updatedb</command> for "
"updating the locate database after entering the root password."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Uppdatera DB</guibutton>: startar <command>updatedb</command> för "
"att uppdatera den lokaliseringsdatabasen efter att systemadministratörens "
"lösenord har matats in."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: closes the locate window."
msgstr "<guibutton>Stäng</guibutton>: Stänger lokaliseringsfönstret."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Results window"
msgstr "Resultatfönster"

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on an item: steps to its folder, makes the item visible and "
"closes the locate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Dubbelklick på ett objekt: Går till dess katalog, gör objektet synligt och "
"stänger lokaliseringsdialogrutan."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right click: edits/views/finds the menu."
msgstr "Högerklick: Redigerar, granskar, visar menyn."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F3</keycap>: views the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F3</keycap>: Granskar aktuellt objekt."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F4</keycap>: edits the current item."
msgstr "<keycap>F4</keycap>: Redigerar aktuellt objekt."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: finds files "
"in the results window."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>: Hittar "
"filer i resultatfönstret."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"next search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>: Visar nästa "
"sökresultat."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: shows the "
"previous search result."
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>: Visar "
"föregående sökresultat."

#. Tag: para
#: locate.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results window supports dragging items to other windows and copy to "
"clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Resultatfönstret stöder att objekt dras till andra fönster och kopieras till "
"klippbordet (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
